@Purwapada I'm always wanting more though, which is why I was a crap student at University and didn't finish my degree, always wanting to study related subjects rather than the one in front of me.

 Regarding that 'related' thing though, I once made an observation that you may like:
The question of whether psychology is a science or a humanity comes up fairly regularly, and I eventually concluded that the answer is 'neither and both' - that it is its _own_ subject and additionally is broad enough to speak to most other subjects - I compress this last into 'Man is the measure of all things" if I want to make it more accessible..
